description: Navigate to 西鉄 赤坂ビル. Head west along the main street, passing the FADIE COFFEE building on your right. Continue straight past the Yamamoto Bunpodo stationery store and the yellow Reganet Cute storefront on your left. The route ends on the sidewalk near the subway entrance, with the destination building on your left.
